PROJECT INSPIRATION

Motion Lexicon was inspired in part by Sam Kalo's public Animation Vocabulary:

https://animations.samkalok.com/

That reference helped demonstrate the value of a shared animation vocabulary. Motion Lexicon independently authors and maintains its current English definitions, canonical mappings, Chinese translations, close-term distinctions, summaries, guidance, previews, prompts, generated outputs, and project code. The linked project does not sponsor or endorse Motion Lexicon.

